MESSAGE.value:
Major restructuring to better support multiple drones.
IandC becomes a DroneHandler object. IandC now steers messages to appropriate DroneHandler, making it if it doesn't exist.
Added dronename to database names in Base.js
Updated main index.html, added /loginPage to app to trigger browser login
Added drone name to the mode constructors, and minor logging changes
Added dashboard for website, based on angular framework
Made own mqtt model with sendUpdates and websockets
Added live chart fragment (with google visualization). This works much better than angular chart for time series
Audio streaming on website appears to be working
Added drone status uploads to website
